ItemDesc: Components used in Xianzhou's ingenium creations. Crude material used for enhancement.
ItemBGDesc: The foundation of Xianzhou's ingenium technology. The smallest constituent of all machine parts. Breaking it apart would be akin to destroying the cellular structure of a living being. "The Intelligentsia Guild put up a bounty of two million credits for technical plans that can flawlessly disassemble Xianzhou mechanical puppets." "If you know Screwllum, then these two millions are basically yours to take..."

ItemComefrom.Desc: Dropped by enemies in Divergent Universe
